      "para_id": "Q001555.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝišzida , his personal god , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , fashioned his own statue , named it for his sake \" ( Gudea ) made the temple worthy of ( Ninĝišzida ) \", and brought it before him into the temple ."
    }
  ],
